title: Silver 4 player LF> duo partner in solo/duo queue to GOLD before end of season
body: I do not feed and I do not type in game. I am looking for a ~~girlfriend~~ I mean duo partner to climb to gold before the season ends.

replies.body: Hi I see you play jinx a lot I am sup jg main love supporting jinx feel free to add me I always buy ss first ward often and communicate with pings good shotcaller.. IGN - TommoTANKS
